author: kfogel
msg: Revert the portion of revision 5663 that broke Subversion on Windows.
(See issue #1294 for wider discussion of the read-onlyness question.)
* subversion/libsvn_subr/io.c
(svn_io_remove_file): Ensure the target is read-write, if SVN_WIN32.
With thanks to Brane for analysis & suggestions.
